    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，CAR到NAMED-DRIVER是一对多的关系。那PERSON这边呢？指定驾驶员应该是和人关联的吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
