    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有一个问题，制造商MANUFACTURER和CAR的关系怎么定？是一个制造商生产多辆车吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
